{
  "stem": "617.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But him being at the age he was, he wasn't really sent far away, because by that time, my father was in his late 30s.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he wasn't sent too far away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was very hard on us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was mostly hard on my mother, having to do everything herself and look after the family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But when he came back, he couldn't start again what-- the way he did, because there were restrictions, like the people he dealt with, some of them weren't sure whether he would be able to deliver because, you know, of all the talk and things, so things started to get a little bit bad and harder.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it wasn't easy to, to make a living there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He came back-- he wasn't long gone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was about six months gone, and then he came back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he picked up from where he left off, but much, much smaller, in a smaller way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because he was called in because he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like, you know, he wasn't in the kind of army that they would give them ammunition.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was in a working army because being a Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, he couldn't-- you couldn't conceal that, being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he-- he-- we took whatever was dished out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't ask questions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you have to, because the authorities there were very strict, and sometimes very corrupt, too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Really not until 1944, spring 1944, right after Passover.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, we were-- the gendarmes came to the home without anything, without any notice, without anything knowing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said in two hours, you'll be taken from your homes, so pack whatever you can and take along food what you have in the house.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
